info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.message_processing.IMessageReceiver

  • Packages that use IMessageReceiver 
    Package Description
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actor_collection_receiver
    Package contains implementation of IMessageReceiver providing collection of actors (stateless actor) by some key.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actor_receiver
    Contains implementation of IMessageReceiver providing synchronization for a receiver that should be executed as actor.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.chain_call_receiver
    Contains implementation of a IMessageReceiver that chooses a IReceiverChain for a message and applies it.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.exception_handling_receivers
    Contains some implementations of IMessageReceiver useful to build chains that will handle exceptions.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.handler_routing_receiver  
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.ireceiver_generator
    Package contains interface for realize class generator for IMessageReceiver
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.irouter
    Contains interface for a router.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.map_router
    Contains implementation of IRouter.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.message_processing
    Contains interfaces related to processing of messages.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.message_processing_sequence
    Contains implementation of info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.imessage_processing_sequence.IMessageProcessingSequence.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.receiver_chain
    Contains simple implementation of info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.ireceiver_chain.IReceiverChain.
    info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.receiver_generator
    Package contains implementation of IReceiverGenerator.
